Sentencas: We herein report a thin film deposition of perovskite BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-delta (BCFZY) by pulsed laser depositing (PLD) method for the use as a cathode in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The BCFZY powder was first synthesized via sol-gel method and pelletized to employ it as a target in PLD system.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: As a result, the PLD-deposited thin BCFZY film showed nano-porous morphology and preferred nano-architecture for cathode of SOFCs.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The applicability of the thin film BCFZY to SOFC cathode was even confirmed by fabricating an SOFC with BCFZY cathode and operating it at 500 degrees C, where stable open-circuit voltage of 1.13 V was measured for an hour.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
